rows.label: qst202803_msg0001
rows.name:
You're Misimisi? Hello there!
We're here because Digidigi said...

rows.label: qst202803_msg0004
rows.name:
Me hear from Digidigi.
He say you search for new mineral
or some such.

rows.label: qst202803_msg0005
rows.name:
Exactly!
It's always been my dream to discover
a brand-new type of mineral.

rows.label: qst202803_msg0006
rows.name:
Normally, Misimisi have policy of
refuse appraisal for walk-ins, but...

rows.label: qst202803_msg0007
rows.name:
Digidigi vouch for you, so me make
exception. Please no hesitate to
bring minerals if you find any!

rows.label: qst202803_msg0008
rows.name:
Me appraise for free, and even
pay little something for it if friends
bring something good.

rows.label: qst202803_msg0010
rows.name:
Why so surprised?
Stingy Nopon is rarity these days.

rows.label: qst202803_msg0011
rows.name:
Master Tora, I think you meant
the opposite of what you said...

rows.label: qst202803_msg0012
rows.name:
Misimisi not speak to you!
Friend Meno is exception, me said!

rows.label: qst202803_msg0014
rows.name:
I hope you like appraising stones,
because I know I'll be bringing you lots!

rows.label: qst202803_msg0015
rows.name:
But first I'll have to find them,
the rare minerals from deposits
all over the world...
